---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about LocalAI Finance - our mission to teach trading through AI-powered education and gamified progression. Meet the 5 AI agents that guide your trading journey."
>
  <Navigation slot="navigation" />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section bg-dark relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-mesh"></div>

    <div class="container-custom relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="font-display text-accent text-sm tracking-widest uppercase block mb-4">
          ü§ñ About LocalAI Finance
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-hero font-display font-bold gradient-text mb-6">
          The Only Platform That Won't Let You Lose Money Until You Prove You Can Make It
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-light-muted mb-8">
          We're solving the biggest problem in trading education: 95% of traders fail because they're thrown into markets without proper training, support, or risk management.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Problem Section -->
  <section class="section-compact bg-dark-lighter">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-section-title font-display font-bold gradient-text mb-6 text-center">
          Why We Built This
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-light mb-12">
          <p class="text-lg">
            Traditional trading platforms have a dirty secret: <strong class="text-primary">they profit when you trade more, not when you succeed</strong>. That's why they use casino-style gamification with confetti, streaks, and push notifications designed to make you trade impulsively.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg">
            Educational courses take the opposite approach - hundreds of hours of theory with zero practice. You learn concepts but never develop the muscle memory and real-time decision-making skills that separate profitable traders from the 95% who fail.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg">
            <strong class="text-accent">We needed something different.</strong> A platform that:
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg list-none ml-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-success text-xl">‚úì</span>
              <span>Forces you to learn fundamentals before risking capital</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-success text-xl">‚úì</span>
              <span>Provides AI-powered guidance at every step</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-success text-xl">‚úì</span>
              <span>Makes you prove competency through paper trading</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-success text-xl">‚úì</span>
              <span>Only allows live trading when you've earned it</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The 5 AI Agents Section -->
  <section class="section bg-dark">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="font-display text-primary text-sm tracking-widest uppercase block mb-2">
          ü§ñ Your AI Trading Team
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-section-title font-display font-bold gradient-text mb-4">
          Meet the 5 AI Agents
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-light-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Each agent specializes in a different aspect of trading. Together, they provide professional-grade analysis and guidance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <!-- Market Data Agent -->
        <div class="glass-card border-l-4 border-warning">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-warning to-amber-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-glow-warning">
              <span class="text-3xl">üì°</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-warning mb-2">
                1. Market Data Agent
              </h3>
              <p class="text-light-muted mb-4">
                <strong class="text-light">What it does:</strong> Collects and validates real-time market data from multiple sources, ensuring accuracy and reliability for all other agents.
              </p>
              <p class="text-light-muted mb-4">
                <strong class="text-light">When you get it:</strong> Level 1+ - The foundation layer, always active.
              </p>
              <p class="text-light-muted">
                <strong class="text-light">Example output:</strong> "AAPL: $175.23 (‚Üë0.8%) | Vol: 52.3M | Data quality: 98% | Sources: 3/3 online | Last update: 2s ago"
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pattern Agent -->
        <div class="glass-card border-l-4 border-success">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-success rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-glow-success">
              <span class="text-3xl">üéØ</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-success mb-2">
                2. Pattern Agent
              </h3>
              <p class="text-light-muted mb-4">
                <strong class="text-light">What it does:</strong> Scans charts 24/7 to recognize technical patterns like double bottoms, head and shoulders, flags, and more.
              </p>
              <p class="text-light-muted mb-4">
                <strong class="text-light">When you get it:</strong> Level 10+ - Unlocked after demonstrating pattern recognition skills.
              </p>
              <p class="text-light-muted">
                <strong class="text-light">Example output:</strong> "Cup and handle forming on TSLA 4H chart. Handle consolidating near $245. Breakout above $248 targets $265 (10% potential). Volume confirms pattern."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Risk Agent -->
        <div class="glass-card border-l-4 border-secondary">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary to-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-glow-purple">
              <span class="text-3xl">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-secondary mb-2">
                3. Risk Agent
              </h3>
              <p class="text-light-muted mb-4">
                <strong class="text-light">What it does:</strong> Monitors your portfolio in real-time, calculates position sizes, sets stop losses, and sends alerts before you overtrade.
              </p>
              <p class="text-light-muted mb-4">
                <strong class="text-light">When you get it:</strong> Level 20+ - Unlocked when you're ready for paper trading.
              </p>
              <p class="text-light-muted">
                <strong class="text-light">Example output:</strong> "‚ö†Ô∏è Portfolio risk at 85% of limit. Reduce NVDA position to 3% or skip this trade. Current exposure: Tech 45%, Energy 20%, Finance 15%."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Backtest Agent -->
        <div class="glass-card border-l-4 border-accent">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-accent rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-glow-cyan">
              <span class="text-3xl">üìä</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-accent mb-2">
                4. Backtest Agent
              </h3>
              <p class="text-light-muted mb-4">
                <strong class="text-light">What it does:</strong> Tests your trading strategies against years of historical data to validate performance before you risk real money.
              </p>
              <p class="text-light-muted mb-4">
                <strong class="text-light">When you get it:</strong> Level 30+ - Unlocked after proving basic market knowledge.
              </p>
              <p class="text-light-muted">
                <strong class="text-light">Example output:</strong> "Your strategy returned 23.4% in 2023 with max drawdown of 8.2%. Win rate: 58%. Best performing during Q1 and Q4. Struggled in choppy summer markets."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Advisor Agent -->
        <div class="glass-card border-l-4 border-primary">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-glow">
              <span class="text-3xl">üß†</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-primary mb-2">
                5. Advisor Agent
              </h3>
              <p class="text-light-muted mb-4">
                <strong class="text-light">What it does:</strong> Analyzes current market conditions, identifies trends, and provides trade recommendations based on insights from all other agents.
              </p>
              <p class="text-light-muted mb-4">
                <strong class="text-light">When you get it:</strong> Level 40+ - The culmination of your journey, synthesizing all agents.
              </p>
              <p class="text-light-muted">
                <strong class="text-light">Example output:</strong> "Strong bullish signal on AAPL. RSI at 42 (oversold), breaking above 50-day MA with increasing volume. Consider entry at $175.20 with stop loss at $172.50."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How They Work Together -->
  <section class="section-compact bg-dark-lighter">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-section-title font-display font-bold gradient-text mb-6 text-center">
          How the Agents Work Together
        </h2>

        <div class="glass-card p-8">
          <div class="space-y-6 text-light">
            <p class="text-lg">
              Imagine you're considering a trade on Apple (AAPL):
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4 ml-6">
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="text-warning font-display font-bold">1.</span>
                <p><strong class="text-warning">Market Data Agent</strong> collects real-time price data for AAPL from multiple sources, validates accuracy, and provides a 98% data quality score.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="text-success font-display font-bold">2.</span>
                <p><strong class="text-success">Pattern Agent</strong> confirms a bullish flag pattern forming on the 1-hour chart with a clear breakout level.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="text-secondary font-display font-bold">3.</span>
                <p><strong class="text-secondary">Risk Agent</strong> calculates you should risk no more than 2% of your portfolio ($400 if you have $20,000), suggests position size of 22 shares at $175, and sets stop loss at $167.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="text-accent font-display font-bold">4.</span>
                <p><strong class="text-accent">Backtest Agent</strong> runs your strategy against AAPL's historical data and shows it would have returned 18% over the past year with this setup.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <span class="text-primary font-display font-bold">5.</span>
                <p><strong class="text-primary">Advisor Agent</strong> synthesizes all the data and identifies AAPL is showing bullish momentum based on recent earnings, technical indicators, and confirmed patterns.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-lg text-center mt-8 text-accent">
              <strong>You make the final decision, but you're not alone.</strong>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="section bg-dark">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-section-title font-display font-bold gradient-text mb-6">
          Our Mission
        </h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-light mb-8">
          To create the <strong class="text-primary">most ethical, effective, and educational</strong> trading platform in the world. One that respects your intelligence, values your time, and actually wants you to succeed.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
          <div class="glass-card text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üéì</div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Education First</h3>
            <p class="text-light-muted text-sm">
              Mandatory learning before trading. No shortcuts.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass-card text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">ü§ñ</div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-accent mb-2">AI-Powered</h3>
            <p class="text-light-muted text-sm">
              Professional-grade analysis accessible to everyone.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass-card text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">‚öñÔ∏è</div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-success mb-2">Ethical Design</h3>
            <p class="text-light-muted text-sm">
              No dark patterns, no gambling mechanics, just results.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12">
          <a href="/beta" class="btn btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
            Join the Beta Waitlist
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>
